Haemish <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#871f78><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/udraevenarmitage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DraevenArmitage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/1/01 11:33:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What Realm? </span><hr size=1> I'm entirely undecided.. really.. mostly..<br>
<br>
Well, my beef is, there is no class in Albion that fits me really.. Scouts, Mercenary..  Well, while they have some of what I want, they just don't have everything I want<br>
<br>
I know, I'm probably asking a lot.<br>
<br>
I've looked over the info for Midguard's Hunter, and only one thing sticks out at me, the use of spears as primary weaponry.. I prefer a sword, but eh, whatever is whatever.  Due to the whole Spear thing, and the &quot;Flavor&quot; of the Midguard realm, they I guess are my second choice..<br>
<br>
First choice, I think is Hibernia.. The Ranger class looks to be fairly good.  While I don't get the logic of making ALL their self buffs only, nothing else, they do have tracking, and a few other skills I like.  Give Rangers a heal spell (May have, not sure) and even a very small pet, and I'm extremely happy.  Still, I dont' know enough about the classes yet to be sure.  The style of the realm however is rather nice, and I think goes well with my personality, It's looking to be a second choice too.<br>
<br>
Albion is dead last, for reasons stated above, but I could deal with it if I had to.. I'd never be truly happy with it however.. (Unless Mercs got Track, then maybe ^_^)<br>
<br>
Yep, no first choice in there.. I don't know enough just yet to make one.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#871f78><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/ugamlaen0.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gamlaen0</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/1/01 12:30:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What Realm? </span><hr size=1> Woot! our own little section! Yeeehhaaaaa! <br>
