<br>
Now, each week, we label that week as Albion Week... i.e. that's the week we focus 4 days out of 7 on our Albion Characters. 4 of the days you'd need to play in Albion on the chosen Albion server, the other 3 days, play what you want. Then the next week, we go to Hibernia, then to Midgard the week after. <br>
<br>
The problem with this that I see is that it would dilute our progress in the short run, but make us very knowledgeable of all the realms in the long run. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
