<br>
I could play something in any realm. A Celtic Champion/Hero, a Viking Berzerker, or a Highlander Armsman. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  See a pattern? <br>
