 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#871f78><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/ugamlaen0.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gamlaen0</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/1/01 1:54:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What Realm? </span><hr size=1> I would just like to reiterate what atton just said...I CAN find a character to play in ANY of the 3 realms...not a biggie to me.  But like he also said, I would like to see us choose a PRIMARY realm that we spend the majority of our time.  Honestly, it doesn't really matter to me at all.<br>
<br>
