 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#871f78><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/uhaemish.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haemish</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/1/01 2:21:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.godwinclients.com/sd/haemish.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What Realm? </span><hr size=1> I have to admit, that for the most part, I've done the same thing as Drae... I don't play alts in Everquest. The time you've seen me devote to it has been on Haemish for about 90% of it, and in the last year, that's been about it. The other classes in EQ just didn't hold enough interest for me. <br>
